data.description: *MOTIVATED SELLER*First time home buyers this is the house for you, a great location only minutes away from interstate 400. This beautiful end until has so much natural light that no physical lighting is needed during the day. Enter through the ground level foyer and take the walk upstairs to the main level. The large open family room features a fire place with sight lines into the kitchen. The kitchen features a breakfast bar with lots of countertop space and a pantry. Tons of storage for all of your family needs. The dining has more of that natural light with access to the deck. Upstairs features the owners suite that has a large walk-in closet and bath. The owners bathroom was updated with new tile floors and vanities with a large spa tub. The bedroom down the hall features an attached bathroom and closet. The lower level has the potential for another bedroom with bathroom. Also there's a fenced in black yard which is great for those with animals. So much potential when it comes to equity and appreciation. A great opportunity for a new homeowner.
